<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>4989(사구팔구) - 메인 장터</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>

<% if (user) { %>
  <body style="font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', dotum, sans-serif; 
               background-color: white; 
               min-height: 100vh; 
               position: relative; 
               overflow-x: hidden; 
               z-index: 1;">
               
    <div style="position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; z-index: -1; pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.07; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-around; padding: 2vh 0;">
      
      <div class="marquee-wrapper">
        <div class="marquee-content text-primary fw-bold" style="animation-duration: 25s;">
          ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="marquee-wrapper">
        <div class="marquee-content text-info fw-bold animate-reverse" style="animation-duration: 30s;">
          ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="marquee-wrapper">
        <div class="marquee-content text-success fw-bold" style="animation-duration: 35s;">
          ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="marquee-wrapper">
        <div class="marquee-content text-warning fw-bold animate-reverse" style="animation-duration: 28s;">
          ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; ✨ <%= user.name %> 상인님! 사구팔구 마켓에 돌아오신 걸 환영합니다. 🛒 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      .marquee-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        overflow: hidden;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
      .marquee-content {
        display: inline-block;
        font-size: 3.5rem; /* 배경 텍스트 크기 */
        animation: textLoop linear infinite;
      }
      .animate-reverse {
        animation: textLoopReverse linear infinite;
      }

      /* 우에서 좌로 흐르는 애니메이션 */
      @keyframes textLoop {
        0% { transform: translateX(0%); }
        100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
      }
      /* 좌에서 우로 흐르는 애니메이션 */
      @keyframes textLoopReverse {
        0% { transform: translateX(-50%); }
        100% { transform: translateX(0%); }
      }
    </style>
<% } else { %>
  <body style="font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', dotum, sans-serif; 
               background-color: #f4f6f9; 
               background-image: radial-gradient(#dcdcdc 1px, transparent 1px); 
               background-size: 20px 20px; 
               min-height: 100vh;">
<% } %>

  <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark mb-4 shadow-sm py-3">
    <div class="container d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold fs-4" href="/">🛒 4989(사구팔구)</a>
      <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
        
        <% if (user) { %>
          <span class="text-light-50 small me-2 text-secondary">상인: <strong class="text-white"><%= user.name %></strong>(<%= user.id %>)</span>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-primary fw-bold" href="/mypage">마이페이지</a>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-info fw-bold text-white" href="/wallet">내 지갑</a>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-warning fw-bold" href="/market/cart">장바구니</a>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-success fw-bold" href="/product/create">물품 내놓기</a>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger" href="/auth/logout">로그아웃</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <span class="text-light-50 small me-2 text-secondary">접속 상태: <strong class="text-warning">게스트</strong></span>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-success fw-bold" href="/auth/login"><i class="bi bi-box-arrow-in-right"></i> 로그인</a>
          <a class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-light fw-bold" href="/auth/register">회원가입</a>
        <% } %>

      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container my-4">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-4 p-4 border border-secondary-subtle mb-4 shadow-sm" style="box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.03);">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <h5 class="fw-bold m-0 text-dark">
            ✨ 안녕하세요, <span class="text-primary"><%= user ? user.name : '방문자' %></span> 상인님!
          </h5>
          <small class="text-muted">오늘도 즐거운 마켓 거래를 시작해보세요.</small>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 text-center border-end">
          <span class="text-muted small d-block">보유 가상 현금</span>
          <strong class="text-dark fs-5"><%= user ? user.cash.toLocaleString() : 0 %>원</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3 text-center">
          <span class="text-muted small d-block">보유 크레딧</span>
          <strong class="text-warning fs-5"><%= user ? user.credit.toLocaleString() : 0 %> P</strong>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-4 p-3 border border-secondary-subtle mb-4 shadow-sm">
      <form action="/friend/add" method="POST" class="row g-2 align-items-center">
        <div class="col-auto">
          <span class="fw-bold text-dark small"><i class="bi bi-person-plus-fill text-primary"></i> 다른 사용자 친구추가 :</span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-3">
          <input type="text" name="friendId" class="form-control form-control-sm" placeholder="상대방 ID 입력" required>
        </div>
        <div class="col-auto">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary fw-bold px-3">친구 등록</button>
        </div>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white rounded-4 p-4 p-md-5 border border-secondary-subtle" style="box-shadow: 0 10px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);">
      
      <div class="mb-5">
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4"><i class="bi bi-star-fill text-warning"></i> 내 친구 상인들의 최신 물품 <span class="text-muted small fs-6">(최대 3개)</span></h4>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4">
          <% if (friendProducts.length === 0) { %>
            <div class="col-12 text-center py-4 border rounded-3 bg-light text-muted">
              등록된 친구 상인의 물품이 없거나 친구가 없습니다.
            </div>
          <% } else { %>
            <% friendProducts.forEach(function(product) { %>
              <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100 border rounded-4 overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white">
                  <div style="height: 200px; background-color: #fff;" class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center border-bottom">
                    <img src="<%= product.image %>" style="max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain;" alt="상품 이미지">
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                    <div>
                      <h5 class="card-title fw-bold text-dark text-truncate mb-1"><%= product.title %></h5>
                      <p class="card-text text-danger fw-bold m-0">
                        <%= product.stock === 0 ? '품절' : product.price.toLocaleString() + '원' %>
                      </p>
                      <small class="text-muted d-block mt-2">판매자: <%= product.writer %></small>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/product/<%= product._id %>" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary w-100 fw-bold mt-3 <%= product.stock === 0 ? 'disabled btn-secondary text-white' : '' %>">
                      <%= product.stock === 0 ? '구매 불가' : '보러가기' %>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% }) %>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="my-5 opacity-25">

      <div>
        <h4 class="fw-bold text-dark mb-4"><i class="bi bi-megaphone-fill text-danger"></i> 전체 판매 물품 목록</h4>
        <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-4 g-4">
          <% if (allProducts.length === 0) { %>
            <div class="col-12 text-center py-5 text-muted">등록된 상품이 없습니다.</div>
          <% } else { %>
            <% allProducts.forEach(function(product) { %>
              <div class="col">
                <div class="card h-100 border rounded-4 overflow-hidden shadow-sm bg-white">
                  <div style="height: 180px; background-color: #fff;" class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center border-bottom">
                    <img src="<%= product.image %>" style="max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; object-fit: contain;" alt="상품 이미지">
                  </div>
                  <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
                    <div>
                      <h6 class="card-title fw-bold text-dark text-truncate mb-1"><%= product.title %></h6>
                      <p class="card-text text-danger fw-bold small m-0">
                        <%= product.stock === 0 ? '품절' : product.price.toLocaleString() + '원' %>
                      </p>
                      <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border mt-2 small">상인: <%= product.writer %></span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/product/<%= product._id %>" class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary w-100 fw-bold mt-3 <%= product.stock === 0 ? 'disabled' : '' %>">
                      <%= product.stock === 0 ? '품절' : '상세보기' %>
                    </a>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% }) %>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div> 
  </div> 

  <footer class="text-center py-4 text-muted border-top bg-white mt-5 small">
    &copy; 2026 4989(사구팔구) 이진혁 이서준 문지송 | All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>